text: cart mein chole bhature bhi daal do
thali add kar do cart mein
dosa add karna hai cart mein
spring roll add karo cart mein
isko cart mein add kar do bhai
koi code hai apply karne ke liye
paisa kat gaya order nahi hua
OTP nahi aa raha payment ka
wallet se pay nahi ho raha
bank se paise wapas nahi aaye
